project.name: ZOS Open Tools
project.description:
A mainframe community effort to port open source tools to a mainframe operating system (called z/OS).
There are ~100 ports now, at https://github.com/zosOpenTools/.
The intent is to make desirable open source projects work on z/OS, and upstream platform and OS-specific patches to the respective projects.
project.license_type: Depends on the license of the project being ported
